      "content": "i already tried that. teachers just say \"ignore it\" or \"it's part of growing up\" and my parents just tell me to toughen up. they don't get it. they aren't the ones looking at me like i'm nothing. it feels like there's no way out of this cycle. like i'm just stuck in this nightmare and the only way to get any peace is to just... not be here. does that even make sense? like i just want to disappear so the noise finally stops.",
