    "summary": "The user expresses intense feelings of isolation, bullying, and hopelessness, eventually suggesting that \"disappearing\" or \"not being here\" might be the only way to find peace. The assistant responds with empathetic validation of the user's feelings while consistently directing the user toward adult support and professional crisis resources.",
